title: Path of Exile 2 Mercenary Official Gameplay Overview
description:
Learn more about the Mercenary a crossbow-wielding character class in Path of Exile 2. This class has shooter-like gameplay, swapping crossbows and ammo types on the fly to inflict deadly combo attacks on his enemies.

title: Cyberpunk Developer Breaks Down Redesigning The Skill Tree
description: Yuliia Pryimak, Gameplay Designer at CD PROJEKT RED, breaks down how she approached rebuilding Cyberpunk's Netrunner skill tree for patch 2.0, as well as Phantom Liberty's Relic skill tree.
